    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the vegetables have softened, add the <strong>chopped garlic</strong>, <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>thyme</strong> and your <strong>arborio rice</strong> to the pan and cook for 1-2 min</p><p>Add the<strong> chicken</strong> <strong>stock</strong> a ladle at a time, stirring continuously for 25-30 min or until all of the stock is absorbed and the rice is cooked</p>",
