      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the rice is cooked, return the <strong>browned chicken</strong> to the pan, stir in your <strong>soft cheese</strong> with <strong>half</strong> of the <strong>grated</strong> <strong>cheddar </strong>(save the rest for garnish!) and cook for 5-7 min further or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>chicken, mushroom & thyme risotto</strong></p>",
