      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>chicken, mushroom & thyme risotto</strong> and sprinkle over the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>grated cheese</strong></p><p>Season with a generous grind of<strong> black pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
